r />\n簽約個陣老闆見證簽名 仲首肯確認你係員工<br />\n點知9個月後 母公司不由分說 話你個簽名冇效 所以要你嘔返9個月人工"},{"pid":"adce9e0e4e4d1c59fe2cfeaa72b459a89a7296e4","tid":337631,"uid":37281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d12086a6fbf6ba1690cdccb3881620e8e585cca1","tid":337631,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"點解請人條友確認請人，但係出左事唔使負責？"},{"pid":"79de751c2fae960aec919782ed5e748f7f8a41af","tid":337631,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬做五毛都俾人昆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾睇唔明 仲係度屈毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}